  <brief_title>Long-Term Low-Molecular-Weight Heparin Versus Oral Anticoagulants in Deep Venous Thrombosis</brief_title>
  <official_title>Phase IV, Randomized, Open-Label Trial Comparing Long-Term Subcutaneous Low-Molecular Weight Heparin With Oral Anticoagulant Therapy in the Treatment of Deep Venous Thrombosis</official_title>
  <sponsors>
